Winning numbers drawn in ‘All or Nothing Night’ game
AUSTIN, Texas (AP) _ The winning numbers in Monday evening’s drawing of the Texas Lottery’s “All or Nothing Night” game were:
02-04-06-08-10-12-13-16-18-20-21-24
(two, four, six, eight, ten, twelve, thirteen, sixteen, eighteen, twenty, twenty-one, twenty-four)
